-- CHUNGHWA PICTURE April Sales Fall 38.83% (Table) : 2475 TT
-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 2012-05-08T08:19:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-08/chunghwa-picture-april-sales-fall-38-83-table-2475-tt.html
CHUNGHWA PICTURE said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 38.83% to NT$3,387,500,000 from NT$5,538,227,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales           3,387,500        5,538,227   
YOY%             -38.83%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           13,414,870       20,384,304  
YOY%             -34.19% 
=================================================================
 